&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/USA-CHICAGO-SEPIA-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4333&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/USA-CHICAGO-SEPIA-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- CHICAGO- SEPIA- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;52&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.gayot.com/restaurants/sepia-chicago-il-60661_5ch070804.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-3624&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/MEDIA-GAYOT-OFFER-LOGO2.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;MEDIA- GAYOT- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;79&quot; height=&quot;70&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set in a former print shop from the 1890&rsquo;s in the Fulton River District of Chicago, Sepia has an elegant, contemporary dining room with design elements from the past. Chef Andrew Zimmerman&rsquo;s cuisine can be described as new American cuisine with a chic pedigree, earning &lt;strong&gt;One Michelin Star, 2014 James Beard Finalist Best Chef Great Lakes &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt;&nbsp;Gayot 2014 Top 10 American Restaurants in Chicago&lt;/strong&gt;. Business casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the &lt;a title=&quot;Sepia&quot; href=&quot;http://www.sepiachicago.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Sepia website&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;contact Sepia by phone at &lt;a href=&quot;tel:312-441-1920&quot;&gt;312-441-1920&lt;/a&gt; or email at email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@sepiachicago.com&quot;&gt;info@sepiachicago.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number. Mention any special needs or allergies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm your reservation. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

